ckquote>好想同呢個老女人瘋狂做愛</blockquote><br />\n屌撚到佢個西著火<br />\n燒哂啲閪毛變白虎都仲得<br />\n之後奶西奶腳<br />\n再用精液幫佢做facial<br />\n<br />\n晚晚都要咁做！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"7d7626784c49730c6388ab435d7ccff67f52ac51","tid":133162,"uid":3602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T15:58:25.000Z","msg":"條女好撚柒正"}]}